  "abilities": {
    "core": [
      "Feel No Pain 5+ FACTION: Power from Pain Macro-steroids (Pain): In the Fight phase , when you select this unit to fight, you can spend 1 of your Pain tokens to Empower this unit. While Empowered, melee weapons equipped by models in this unit have a Strength characteristic of 8 and the [LETHAL HITS] ability. Monstrous Charge: Each time this unit ends a Charge move , select one enemy unit within Engagement Range of it, then roll one D6 for each model in this unit that is within Engagement Range of that enemy unit: for each 4+, that enemy unit suffers D3 mortal wounds ."
